    {
      "id": "PopularPost369824",
      "post_content": "@BobbySinclair  \nSpells require legal targets to be cast, so you must control a creature to cast Simularum.  \n  \nComboing with [Stuffy Doll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stuffy Doll), [Boros Reckoner](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Reckoner), or [Spitemare](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spitemare) seems like a good idea. Other than that, [Darkness](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darkness) may be a more effective [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog) for a mono-black deck.",
      "posted_by": "Hua9801",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost369824\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">@BobbySinclair<br/>Spells require legal targets to be cast, so you must control a creature to cast Simularum.<br/><br/>Comboing with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stuffy Doll\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stuffy Doll\">Stuffy Doll</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boros Reckoner\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Reckoner\">Boros Reckoner</a>, or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spitemare\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spitemare\">Spitemare</a> seems like a good idea. Other than that, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Darkness\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darkness\">Darkness</a> may be a more effective <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog\">Fog</a> for a mono-black deck.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '369824'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy87193\">Hua9801</span>\r\n                                (4/5/2014 8:17:57 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div styl